snippet.title: Venus Vacation PRISM - DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
[Teaser Website] https://www.gamecity.com.tw/venusvacation/prism/en/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=teaser&utm_id=Caption

On this island, the moment of love.

A new project from the "Venus Vacation" series
An immersive romantic adventure game, coming early 2025!

Product Information
Title: Venus Vacation PRISM - DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme -
Platforms: PlayStation®5 / PlayStation®4 / Steam®
Release Date: Early 2025
Price: To be determined
Genre: Immersive Romantic Adventure

*Screens are taken from an in-development build.
